Our goal at the smart Baker

00:13:48,295 --> 00:13:50,397
is to make
those bakers' lives easier.

00:13:50,464 --> 00:13:52,766
Since most recipes call
for an amount much too high

00:13:52,833 --> 00:13:55,769
