right out of our garage.

00:14:25,265 --> 00:14:27,000
We've also designed a line
of Parchment paper that

00:14:27,067 --> 00:14:29,436
comes in precut, flat sheets
that are made to fit

00:14:29,503 --> 00:14:31,471
the most common Size
baking Pans.

00:14:31,538 --> 00:14:33,540
Plus, we've added
unique lift tabs that

00:14:33,607 --> 00:14:35,275
put us ahead
of our competitors.

00:14:35,342 --> 00:14:36,610
Oh, good idea.

