made of cardboard,

00:14:42,282 --> 00:14:44,885
the smart Baker's cupcake
and treat tower is reusable

00:14:44,952 --> 00:14:46,753
and made of
washable, durable P.V.C.,

00:14:46,820 --> 00:14:47,921
eliminating the need

00:14:47,988 --> 00:14:50,390
to constantly replace
after every use.

00:14:50,457 --> 00:14:53,293
With your help, we can make
everyone a smart Baker,

00:14:53,360 --> 00:14:55,629
and we'd like you
to be one, too.

00:14:55,696 --> 00:14:57,598
